Crispy Garlic Butter Chicken Thighs

40 min
$12.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Description

Juicy chicken thighs seared to perfection with crispy skin, enriched with aromatic garlic butter.

Ingredients

  • chicken thighs: 4 pieces
  • garlic: 4 cloves
  • butter: 4 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1 teaspoon

  • fresh parsley: 2 tablespoons
